Others: The sixth match of the Bhutan T20I Quadrangular 2024 will feature Bhutan Club versus Indonesia.
Bhutan Club currently occupies third place in the Bhutan T20I Quadrangular 2024 standings, having secured one victory in two matches.
In contrast, Indonesia seeks resurgence, losing both of their encounters to date. This positions them at the bottom of the table.

The impending matchup between Bhutan Club and Indonesia holds significant implications. Bhutan Club aims to solidify its ranking, while Indonesia strives to revive its campaign and climb the standings.
The match is scheduled for October 22 at 1:15 PM IST, taking place at the prestigious Gelephu International Cricket Ground, Gelephu.
